{"tid":917201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長毛：選擇「射落海」或投馮檢基都係巿民選擇「有乜好怨」。","createTime":"2018-11-26T08:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T03:37:39.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b6478e4331ade7adbad4b053f2986aa68e521140","tid":917201,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181126/large/1543219132_5d18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181126%2Flarge%2F1543219132_5d18.jpg&h=25d5c67e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n代表民主派參加九龍西立法會補選的工黨李卓人，最終以過萬票差距輸給建制派候選人陳凱欣，其中有7個票站李卓人得票大幅落後陳凱欣逾20%。李卓人下午3時將在民主派議員陪同下召開記者會，總結今次選戰結果。李卓人認為，要聽取不同人的心聲，包括要票投馮檢基，支持「投白票」、以致「焦土」的選民，希望能爭取他們的選票，在下次立法會選舉捲土重來。<br />\n<br />\n民主派立法會議員與李卓人及被DQ的劉小麗於立法會召開記招並發表聯合聲明，宣佈就今次九龍西補選結果，民主派承認失敗，並對未能挽回選民於政治選舉中的無力感，深表難過及致歉。李卓人與同場的民主派議員向巿民鞠躬致歉，毛孟靜帶領鞠躬時一度哽咽。<br />\n<br />\n民主派在聲明中又指，「我們失望，但不絕望，不言放棄」，指香港民主路仍然漫長，民主派痛定思痛，承諾會繼續奮鬥，希望巿民能與民主派一起並肩作戰，為香港、為民主、為下一代堅持到底。」<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄認為，無論選民決定「射落海」或票投馮檢基，也屬於選民的選擇「有乜好怨」。認為泛民要面對失去選票的問題，他形容只是失去兩個戰役，並不是失去戰爭，而陳凱欣代表的建制派選票並無增加，故呼籲泛民應該團結，在未來的選舉爭取更多支持。"},{"pid":"5aa73f304c9173f9561b7f6113b845b268f5d5d8","tid":917201,"uid":35430,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:58:23.000Z","msg":"意見接受態度照舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfc5166af9940c4121f1cd7ddfa6949f0a2bb50","tid":917201,"uid":60341,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/165734_3abe7b9590b62cc279ef4f88e70e0d29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F165734_3abe7b9590b62cc279ef4f88e70e0d29.png&h=e898db1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩呀，有咩好怨？<br />\n毛哥落旨，寧願輸都唔要啲蛤蟆票"},{"pid":"d2b45e76f8b1e62d61353f3de2b3c3f9733d063b","tid":917201,"uid":115525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:01:37.000Z","msg":"2018 又一次痛定思痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係變年經"},{"pid":"f492d68af72b33e5f9a2c4b6a808227baae72a7e","tid":917201,"uid":153239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:03:18.000Z","msg":"今次到我缺席啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959cd08d0222368813f520fadb5b1838aef43eb2","tid":917201,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Rhh7MHhy/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FRhh7MHhy%2Fimage.jpg&h=2eed08a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fff8773e92ddec40ad845b1d9c0822347820225","tid":917201,"uid":3255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:03:49.000Z","msg":"仲想2020重來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲未知成件事錯係邊"},{"pid":"f1f2df841e574fd9f2c519935573ae814df2a7ff","tid":917201,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/165734_3abe7b9590b62cc279ef4f88e70e0d29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F165734_3abe7b9590b62cc279ef4f88e70e0d29.png&h=e898db1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩呀，有咩好怨？<br />\n毛哥落旨，寧願輸都唔要啲蛤蟆票</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肥共黎黎幫住僭共狗補飛，繼續昆班毒果離地白癡囉！！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88abf7c6e037ec89c8f374a9ed1079267bf8b97","tid":917201,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sc